    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sites considered for development that already have some form of development on them or that are derelict and thus would require clearance before redevelopment could take place.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000016271/Goulty, Dictionary of Landscape (1991)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Te gebruiken voor terreinen die in aanmerking komen voor bebouwing maar waarop al enige vorm van ontwikkeling heeft plaatsgevonden of die vervallen zijn, zodat er eerst moet worden ontruimd of gesloopt voordat nieuwbouw kan plaatsvinden.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000119831/IATE: European Union Terminology (2022-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>作為開發用地，而土地上已有某些形式的開發，或者曾經開發但已遭棄置的土地，因此需要在土地重新開發前，將原有的地面物清除。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gelände, das zur Bebauung vorgesehen ist, das bereits irgendeine Form von Bebauung hat oder diese verfallen ist und deshalb Freimachen erforderlich ist, bevor eine Wiederbebauung stattfinden kann.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
